data.description: *Assumable Loan @ 2.99%* Location, Location, Location! This spacious 5 bedroom home is located nearby shopping, restaurants, hospital, schools, and only 3 miles from the Fort Cavazos Clear Creek Gate! Step inside the foyer and be greeted with a beautiful staircase and a large formal dining area that can also be used as a flex space. A few more steps will bring you into the large living room and open concept kitchen and eat-in kitchen area with enhanced vinyl planking. The kitchen is a chef's dream with double ovens, granite countertops, custom cabinetry and a large pantry. Upstairs holds the primary bedroom suite with a covered balcony and french doors, double vanity, separate shower and tub, and a large walk-in closet. Three large secondary bedrooms, a full bath and a loft area are also located upstairs. There is a 5th bedroom that can also be used as a study located downstairs and a 3rd full bath. Enjoy the outdoors with a large backyard and covered back patio. This home has it all - location, size, style, and NO HOA! Also available for RENT offered at $2600 monthly!
